---
config:
    layout: elk
    look: handDrawn
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Employee as 👤 Employee
    participant MobileApp as 📱 Mobile App
    participant API as 🔌 API Server
    participant Database as 💾 PostgreSQL
    participant Dashboard as 💻 Dashboard
    participant Manager as 👨‍💼 Manager

    rect rgb(200, 220, 255)
    Note over Employee,Dashboard: HAPPY PATH: CHECK-IN PROCESS
    end

    Employee->>MobileApp: Opens app, authenticates with Face ID
    MobileApp->>API: POST /auth/login (Face ID token)
    API->>Database: Verify user credentials (RLS policy)
    Database-->>API: User authenticated ✅
    API-->>MobileApp: Return JWT tokens (30min + 7day)

    Employee->>MobileApp: Scans QR code at site
    MobileApp->>API: POST /api/v1/checkin<br/>{qr_code, timestamp, type: IN}
    API->>Database: ⚠️ VALIDATION (Multi-Tenant):<br/>0. Extract client_id from JWT<br/>1. JWT valid?<br/>2. Employee.client_id = request.client_id?<br/>3. Employee assigned to site?<br/>4. Duplicate (within 60s)?<br/>5. Timestamp < 1min old?

    alt Validation PASSED
        Database->>Database: INSERT check_in record
        Database->>Database: TRIGGER audit_log<br/>(CREATE action)
        Database-->>API: 201 Created<br/>{id, timestamp, type, status}
        API-->>MobileApp: ✅ Check-in successful
        MobileApp->>Employee: Display confirmation
        Database-->>Dashboard: Real-time update (polling, 10s interval)
        Dashboard->>Manager: 🔴 New presence visible
    else Validation FAILED: DUPLICATE
        API-->>MobileApp: 409 Conflict<br/>DUPLICATE_CHECKIN<br/>(within 60 seconds)
        MobileApp->>Employee: ⚠️ Check-in already registered
    else Validation FAILED: NOT ASSIGNED
        API-->>MobileApp: 403 Forbidden<br/>EMPLOYEE_NOT_ASSIGNED
        MobileApp->>Employee: ⚠️ Contact manager
    else Validation FAILED: QR INVALID
        API-->>MobileApp: 404 Not Found<br/>INVALID_QR_CODE
        MobileApp->>Employee: ⚠️ QR code not valid
    end

    rect rgb(255, 220, 200)
    Note over Manager,Dashboard: CORRECTION PROCESS: MANAGER
    end

    Manager->>Dashboard: Notices wrong timestamp in table
    Dashboard->>API: PUT /api/v1/checkins/{checkin_id}<br/>{timestamp, reason}
    API->>Database: 🔍 CHECK CORRECTION WINDOW:<br/>• Manager: can correct 48h old<br/>• Employee: can correct 2h old<br/>• Current: within window?

    alt Window VALID
        Database->>Database: UPDATE check_in<br/>• timestamp = new value<br/>• corrected_at = now<br/>• corrected_by = manager_id<br/>• status = 'corrected'
        Database->>Database: TRIGGER audit_log<br/>(CORRECT action with reason)
        Database-->>API: 200 OK<br/>{id, timestamp, status}
        API-->>Dashboard: ✅ Correction saved
        Dashboard->>Manager: Confirmation ✅<br/>Audit trail recorded
    else Window CLOSED
        API-->>Dashboard: 409 Conflict<br/>CORRECTION_WINDOW_CLOSED<br/>(too old, ask admin)
        Dashboard->>Manager: ⚠️ Too old to correct
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
    Note over Dashboard,Manager: COMPLIANCE: AUDIT TRAIL
    end

    Manager->>Dashboard: View Audit Log
    Dashboard->>API: GET /api/v1/audit?entity=checkin
    API->>Database: SELECT from audit_log<br/>WHERE client_id = current_client<br/>AND entity_id = checkin_id
    Database-->>API: Immutable log entries:<br/>{action, user_id, timestamp, changes}
    API-->>Dashboard: Display audit trail:<br/>✅ CREATE @ 09:15 by Employee<br/>✏️ CORRECT @ 09:18 by Manager<br/>(timestamp: 09:15 → 09:20, reason: wrong time)

    rect rgb(255, 220, 220)
    Note over Dashboard,Manager: GDPR: DATA DELETION & RETENTION
    end

    Manager->>Dashboard: Request employee deletion
    Dashboard->>API: PUT /api/v1/employees/:id/delete<br/>{reason: "Left company"}
    API->>Database: 🔒 GDPR DELETION PROCESS:<br/>1. Mark employee deleted_at = NOW<br/>2. Soft delete all check-ins for employee<br/>3. TRIGGER audit_log (DELETE action)<br/>4. Schedule hard delete after 12 months
    Database-->>API: 200 OK<br/>Deletion scheduled
    API-->>Dashboard: ✅ Employee deleted (12-month retention)
    Dashboard->>Manager: Confirmation:<br/>📋 Employee data will be permanently deleted<br/>📅 Hard delete scheduled: 12 months from now<br/>✅ Audit trail preserved for compliance

    rect rgb(200, 255, 255)
    Note over Dashboard,Manager: REPORTING: CSV EXPORT
    end

    Manager->>Dashboard: Export presences (date range)
    Dashboard->>API: GET /api/v1/export/csv<br/>?from=2026-05-28&to=2026-05-29
    API->>Database: SELECT check_ins with corrections<br/>WHERE client_id = current_client<br/>ORDER BY timestamp DESC
    Database-->>API: Results with status flags<br/>(confirmed vs corrected)
    API-->>Dashboard: CSV file<br/>employee,site,time_in,time_out,status
    Dashboard->>Manager: ⬇️ Download checkins_2026-05-28.csv

    rect rgb(255, 200, 200)
    Note over API,Database: ⏱️ TIMING CONSTRAINTS
    end

    Note over API: • Check-in response: < 500ms<br/>• Duplicate detection: exact 60s window<br/>• Correction window: 2h employee / 48h manager<br/>• Dashboard refresh: real-time (WebSocket) or 10s polling
